References:
Fatal Hypernatremia From Exogenous Salt Intake: Report of a Case and Review of the Literature. https://www.mayoclinicproceedings.org/article/S0025-6196(12)62194-6/fulltext this is not the case from this video. it's a review for students to understand the nature of hypernatremia, and how both  excess exogenous sodium intake coupled with severe water loss contributes to symptomatic hypernatremia.
